OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FWith Humza Yousaf having announced he
OL,7,Fwill stand down as First Minister of
OL,8,FScotland, the PA news agency looks at
OL,9,Fthe likely contenders for the top job.
OL,11,F` John Swinney
OL,13,FThe loyal, deputy first minister to
OL,14,FNicola Sturgeon has said he is
OL,15,F"actively considering" standing to
OL,16,Freplace Mr Yousaf.
