OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHe said he has been "somewhat
OL,7,Foverwhelmed" by the number of party
OL,8,Fcolleagues calling on him to do so,
OL,9,Fwho include senior SNP figures such as
OL,10,FPete Wishart and former Westminster
OL,11,Fleader, Ian Blackford.
OL,13,FMr Swinney has the benefit of
OL,14,Fsignificant experience, having been an
OL,15,FMSP since the Scottish Parliament's
OL,16,Finception in 1999, serving North
OL,17,FTayside, and previously representing
OL,18,Fthe same constituency at Westminster
OL,19,Fin 1997.
