OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FMr Swinney previously led his party in
OL,7,FHolyrood between 2000 and 2004 during
OL,8,Fthe SNP's time on the opposition
OL,9,Fbenches.
OL,11,FHe has held a raft of cabinet
OL,12,Fpositions, including education and
OL,13,Ffinance and resigned at the same time
OL,14,Fas Ms Sturgeon.
OL,16,FHe ruled himself out of the 2023
OL,17,Fleadership race, stating he had to put
OL,18,Fhis young family first.
