OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHowever, the SNP politician could take
OL,7,Fthe reins to unite his party in a time
OL,8,Fof turmoil.
OL,10,F` Kate Forbes
OL,12,FThe Skye, Lochaber and Badenoch MSP
OL,13,Fnarrowly lost to Mr Yousaf in the
OL,14,Ffiery leadership contest to replace Ms
OL,15,FSturgeon just over a year ago.
