OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FAnd as finance secretary under Ms
OL,7,FSturgeon, Ms Forbes has been known to
OL,8,Fhelp her government through tough
OL,9,Fcrises, stepping into the role and
OL,10,Fdelivering a budget at short notice
OL,11,Fafter her predecessor, Derek Mackay,
OL,12,Fresigned in disgrace in 2020.
OL,14,FA Free Church of Scotland member, Ms
OL,15,FForbes' first run at the leadership
OL,16,Fwas not smooth sailing as her stance
OL,17,Fon social issues was at odds with many
OL,18,Fwithin her own party, particularly her
OL,19,Fopposition to gender reform.
