OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,F` Neil Gray
OL,8,FThe wealth of experience held by Neil
OL,9,FGray could make him a likely contender
OL,10,Ffor leadership.
OL,12,FHe is thought to be the closest ally
OL,13,Fof Mr Yousaf but may be able to unite
OL,14,FParliament.
OL,16,FHe is a former MP and became an MSP in
OL,17,F2021 serving as a culture and
OL,18,Finternational development minister
OL,19,Fbefore being promoted to Economy, Fair
OL,20,FWork and Energy Secretary around a
OL,21,Fyear later.
