OL,6,FHe stepped up to become Health
OL,7,FSecretary following the resignation of
OL,8,FMichael Matheson.
OL,10,F` Jenny Gilruth
OL,12,FFormer teacher Jenny Gilruth
OL,13,Frepresents Mid Fife and Glenrothes and
OL,14,Fis the current Education Secretary.
OL,16,FHer brief is one of the toughest as
OL,17,Fshe faces pressure to address the
OL,18,Fincreasing issue of violence in
OL,19,Fschools.
